{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/shader_programming_intro_2/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>본 포스팅은 Pope Kim의 『셰이더 프로그래밍 입문 (한빛미디어, 2012)』의 Part 1의 Chapter 2에 해당하는 내용(p. 46-74)을 요약하기 위해 작성되었다.</p>\n<h2>Pope Kim의 셰이더의 정의</h2>\n<p>\"화면에 출력할 <strong>픽셀</strong>의 <strong>위치</strong>와 <strong>색상</strong>을 계산하는 함수.\"</p>\n<h2>학습 목표</h2>\n<p><strong>진짜 쉬운 빨강 셰이더</strong>를 직접 만들어봄으로써 \"화면에 출력할 픽셀의 위치와 색상을 계산하는 함수\"로서의 셰이더를 작성하고 그 구조와 활용법을 이해할 수 있다.</p>\n<h2>\"진짜 쉬운 빨강 셰이더\" 만들기</h2>\n<h3>개발 환경 설정: 바닥부터 만들기</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://gpuopen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/RenderMonkey.2008-12-17-v1.82.322.msi.zip\">렌더몽키</a>를 설치한다</li>\n<li>렌더몽키를 실행한다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7100210f71e777096f931001b48556f6/9b29b/render_monkey_startup.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"render_monkey_startup\"\n        title=\"render_monkey_startup\"\n        src=\"/static/7100210f71e777096f931001b48556f6/5a190/render_monkey_startup.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7100210f71e777096f931001b48556f6/772e8/render_monkey_startup.png 200w,\n/static/7100210f71e777096f931001b48556f6/e17e5/render_monkey_startup.png 400w,\n/static/7100210f71e777096f931001b48556f6/5a190/render_monkey_startup.png 800w,\n/static/7100210f71e777096f931001b48556f6/c1b63/render_monkey_startup.png 1200w,\n/static/7100210f71e777096f931001b48556f6/29007/render_monkey_startup.png 1600w,\n/static/7100210f71e777096f931001b48556f6/9b29b/render_monkey_startup.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Effect Workspace 오른쪽 클릭 > Add Default Effect > DirectX > DirectX 메뉴 선택</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c9bbf59c6c201cb6d2451612bd708c2f/9b29b/add_default_effect_directx_directx.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"add_default_effect_directx_directx\"\n        title=\"add_default_effect_directx_directx\"\n        src=\"/static/c9bbf59c6c201cb6d2451612bd708c2f/5a190/add_default_effect_directx_directx.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c9bbf59c6c201cb6d2451612bd708c2f/772e8/add_default_effect_directx_directx.png 200w,\n/static/c9bbf59c6c201cb6d2451612bd708c2f/e17e5/add_default_effect_directx_directx.png 400w,\n/static/c9bbf59c6c201cb6d2451612bd708c2f/5a190/add_default_effect_directx_directx.png 800w,\n/static/c9bbf59c6c201cb6d2451612bd708c2f/c1b63/add_default_effect_directx_directx.png 1200w,\n/static/c9bbf59c6c201cb6d2451612bd708c2f/29007/add_default_effect_directx_directx.png 1600w,\n/static/c9bbf59c6c201cb6d2451612bd708c2f/9b29b/add_default_effect_directx_directx.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>이제 다음과 같이 빨간 공이 별도의 창에 출력될 것이다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a6180c07fd6f93a89c53f98301f69c6c/9b29b/default_directx_effect.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"default_directx_effect\"\n        title=\"default_directx_effect\"\n        src=\"/static/a6180c07fd6f93a89c53f98301f69c6c/5a190/default_directx_effect.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a6180c07fd6f93a89c53f98301f69c6c/772e8/default_directx_effect.png 200w,\n/static/a6180c07fd6f93a89c53f98301f69c6c/e17e5/default_directx_effect.png 400w,\n/static/a6180c07fd6f93a89c53f98301f69c6c/5a190/default_directx_effect.png 800w,\n/static/a6180c07fd6f93a89c53f98301f69c6c/c1b63/default_directx_effect.png 1200w,\n/static/a6180c07fd6f93a89c53f98301f69c6c/29007/default_directx_effect.png 1600w,\n/static/a6180c07fd6f93a89c53f98301f69c6c/9b29b/default_directx_effect.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>우리는 특정 색(빨강)을 출력하는 셰이더를 만들 것이기 때문에 이펙트의 이름을 기본값인 \"Default_DirectX_Effect\"에서 \"ColorShader\"로 변경한다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/88f6df3be58e05a3e6b35a1c17e7fe19/9b29b/rename_default_directx_effect.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"rename_default_directx_effect\"\n        title=\"rename_default_directx_effect\"\n        src=\"/static/88f6df3be58e05a3e6b35a1c17e7fe19/5a190/rename_default_directx_effect.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/88f6df3be58e05a3e6b35a1c17e7fe19/772e8/rename_default_directx_effect.png 200w,\n/static/88f6df3be58e05a3e6b35a1c17e7fe19/e17e5/rename_default_directx_effect.png 400w,\n/static/88f6df3be58e05a3e6b35a1c17e7fe19/5a190/rename_default_directx_effect.png 800w,\n/static/88f6df3be58e05a3e6b35a1c17e7fe19/c1b63/rename_default_directx_effect.png 1200w,\n/static/88f6df3be58e05a3e6b35a1c17e7fe19/29007/rename_default_directx_effect.png 1600w,\n/static/88f6df3be58e05a3e6b35a1c17e7fe19/9b29b/rename_default_directx_effect.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>이제 이후의 학습을 위해 기존 셰이더 코드를 지우고 변수를 삭제한다. 좌측의 Workspace 창에서 \"Pass 0\" 항목을 찾아 그 옆의 '+ (확장)' 버튼을 누르면 정점 셰이더(Vertex Shader)와 픽셀 셰이더(Pixel Shader) 항목이 자식으로 포함되어 있는 것을 알 수 있다. 이 두 코드의 내용을 일괄 선택한 뒤 깨끗이 삭제한다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/14555e7864e39d362019cea7f7be62cd/9b29b/remove_existing_shader.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"remove_existing_shader\"\n        title=\"remove_existing_shader\"\n        src=\"/static/14555e7864e39d362019cea7f7be62cd/5a190/remove_existing_shader.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/14555e7864e39d362019cea7f7be62cd/772e8/remove_existing_shader.png 200w,\n/static/14555e7864e39d362019cea7f7be62cd/e17e5/remove_existing_shader.png 400w,\n/static/14555e7864e39d362019cea7f7be62cd/5a190/remove_existing_shader.png 800w,\n/static/14555e7864e39d362019cea7f7be62cd/c1b63/remove_existing_shader.png 1200w,\n/static/14555e7864e39d362019cea7f7be62cd/29007/remove_existing_shader.png 1600w,\n/static/14555e7864e39d362019cea7f7be62cd/9b29b/remove_existing_shader.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>변수 삭제의 경우는, 좌측의 Workspace 창에서 \"matViewProjection\"을 선택한 뒤 \"Delete\"를 클릭해 삭제해주면 된다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3b9b9b3918caec5f00c30e803463b2e6/9b29b/remove_existing_variable.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"remove_existing_variable\"\n        title=\"remove_existing_variable\"\n        src=\"/static/3b9b9b3918caec5f00c30e803463b2e6/5a190/remove_existing_variable.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3b9b9b3918caec5f00c30e803463b2e6/772e8/remove_existing_variable.png 200w,\n/static/3b9b9b3918caec5f00c30e803463b2e6/e17e5/remove_existing_variable.png 400w,\n/static/3b9b9b3918caec5f00c30e803463b2e6/5a190/remove_existing_variable.png 800w,\n/static/3b9b9b3918caec5f00c30e803463b2e6/c1b63/remove_existing_variable.png 1200w,\n/static/3b9b9b3918caec5f00c30e803463b2e6/29007/remove_existing_variable.png 1600w,\n/static/3b9b9b3918caec5f00c30e803463b2e6/9b29b/remove_existing_variable.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li>이제 새로운 셰이더 코드를 바닥부터 작성할 준비가 끝났다</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>전역 변수의 선언</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>우선 전역 변수로 사용할 월드 행렬(World Matrix), 뷰 행렬(View Matrix), 투영 행렬(Projection Matrix)를 차례대로 만든다. 일단 다음과 같이 float4x4 타입의 행렬을 하나 만든다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/720ceacc1856cbce2c6e9c5421a64ce8/9b29b/create_global_matrix_variables.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"create_global_matrix_variables\"\n        title=\"create_global_matrix_variables\"\n        src=\"/static/720ceacc1856cbce2c6e9c5421a64ce8/5a190/create_global_matrix_variables.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/720ceacc1856cbce2c6e9c5421a64ce8/772e8/create_global_matrix_variables.png 200w,\n/static/720ceacc1856cbce2c6e9c5421a64ce8/e17e5/create_global_matrix_variables.png 400w,\n/static/720ceacc1856cbce2c6e9c5421a64ce8/5a190/create_global_matrix_variables.png 800w,\n/static/720ceacc1856cbce2c6e9c5421a64ce8/c1b63/create_global_matrix_variables.png 1200w,\n/static/720ceacc1856cbce2c6e9c5421a64ce8/29007/create_global_matrix_variables.png 1600w,\n/static/720ceacc1856cbce2c6e9c5421a64ce8/9b29b/create_global_matrix_variables.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>해당 행렬의 변수명을 기본값인 \"f4x4MyMatrix\"에서 \"gWorldMatrix\"로 변경한다. 그리고 렌더몽키에서 제공하는 변수 시멘틱(variable semantic)을 활용해 월드 행렬 값을 대입한다. 월드 행렬 값은 해당 변수를 오른쪽 클릭한 다음 Variable Semantic > World를 선택해 대입해주면 된다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/53706bb789d02dd99ee7274c04f241cd/9b29b/add_world_matrix_w_variable_semantic.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"add_world_matrix_w_variable_semantic\"\n        title=\"add_world_matrix_w_variable_semantic\"\n        src=\"/static/53706bb789d02dd99ee7274c04f241cd/5a190/add_world_matrix_w_variable_semantic.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/53706bb789d02dd99ee7274c04f241cd/772e8/add_world_matrix_w_variable_semantic.png 200w,\n/static/53706bb789d02dd99ee7274c04f241cd/e17e5/add_world_matrix_w_variable_semantic.png 400w,\n/static/53706bb789d02dd99ee7274c04f241cd/5a190/add_world_matrix_w_variable_semantic.png 800w,\n/static/53706bb789d02dd99ee7274c04f241cd/c1b63/add_world_matrix_w_variable_semantic.png 1200w,\n/static/53706bb789d02dd99ee7274c04f241cd/29007/add_world_matrix_w_variable_semantic.png 1600w,\n/static/53706bb789d02dd99ee7274c04f241cd/9b29b/add_world_matrix_w_variable_semantic.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>같은 식으로 \"gViewMatrix\", \"gProjectionMatrix\" 변수를 생성한 뒤 각각 Variable Semantic > View와 Variable Semantic > Projection을 대입한다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e4ee12b4e94ba1082de204dd231201e0/9b29b/create_global_matrix_variables_done.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"create_global_matrix_variables_done\"\n        title=\"create_global_matrix_variables_done\"\n        src=\"/static/e4ee12b4e94ba1082de204dd231201e0/5a190/create_global_matrix_variables_done.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e4ee12b4e94ba1082de204dd231201e0/772e8/create_global_matrix_variables_done.png 200w,\n/static/e4ee12b4e94ba1082de204dd231201e0/e17e5/create_global_matrix_variables_done.png 400w,\n/static/e4ee12b4e94ba1082de204dd231201e0/5a190/create_global_matrix_variables_done.png 800w,\n/static/e4ee12b4e94ba1082de204dd231201e0/c1b63/create_global_matrix_variables_done.png 1200w,\n/static/e4ee12b4e94ba1082de204dd231201e0/29007/create_global_matrix_variables_done.png 1600w,\n/static/e4ee12b4e94ba1082de204dd231201e0/9b29b/create_global_matrix_variables_done.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>이제 셰이더 함수에서 사용할 전역 변수들이 준비되었다</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>정점 셰이더 함수 구현: 위치 구하기</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>이제 본격적으로 셰이더 함수를 구현해보도록 하자. 위에서 우리는 기존의 세이더 코드를 지웠지만 \"Pass 0\" 항목 내의 \"Vertex Shader\" 항목 자체는 남아있을 것이다. 해당 항목을 선택하면 열리는 \"Shader Editor\" 입력창에 코드를 작성해보자</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/286afa9f15f2bac6194e3a906a38ae5a/9b29b/start_writing_new_vertex_shader.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"start_writing_new_vertex_shader\"\n        title=\"start_writing_new_vertex_shader\"\n        src=\"/static/286afa9f15f2bac6194e3a906a38ae5a/5a190/start_writing_new_vertex_shader.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/286afa9f15f2bac6194e3a906a38ae5a/772e8/start_writing_new_vertex_shader.png 200w,\n/static/286afa9f15f2bac6194e3a906a38ae5a/e17e5/start_writing_new_vertex_shader.png 400w,\n/static/286afa9f15f2bac6194e3a906a38ae5a/5a190/start_writing_new_vertex_shader.png 800w,\n/static/286afa9f15f2bac6194e3a906a38ae5a/c1b63/start_writing_new_vertex_shader.png 1200w,\n/static/286afa9f15f2bac6194e3a906a38ae5a/29007/start_writing_new_vertex_shader.png 1600w,\n/static/286afa9f15f2bac6194e3a906a38ae5a/9b29b/start_writing_new_vertex_shader.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>일단 앞에서 생성한 전역 변수를 먼저 선언하도록 하자</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"hlsl\"><pre class=\"language-hlsl\"><code class=\"language-hlsl\"><span class=\"token keyword\">float4x4</span> gWorldMatrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">float4x4</span> gViewMatrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">float4x4</span> gProjectionMatrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>함수는 입력과 출력을 필요로 한다. 따라서 입력과 출력 구조체를 선언하도록 한다</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"hlsl\"><pre class=\"language-hlsl\"><code class=\"language-hlsl\"><span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">VS_INPUT</span> \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span> mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> POSITION<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">VS_OUTPUT</span> \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span> mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> POSITION<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>그 다음, 본격적으로 정점 셰이더 함수를 작성한다</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"hlsl\"><pre class=\"language-hlsl\"><code class=\"language-hlsl\">VS_OUTPUT <span class=\"token function\">vs_main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> VS_INPUT Input <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   VS_OUTPUT Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n   Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> Input<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gWorldMatrix <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>         <span class=\"token comment\">// 월드 행렬로 공간 변환</span>\n   Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gViewMatrix <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>          <span class=\"token comment\">// 뷰 행렬로 공간 변환</span>\n   Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gProjectionMatrix <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// 투영 행렬로 공간 변환</span>\n   \n   <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">error X3000: syntax error: unexpected token &#39;struct&#39;</code> 에러가 발생하는 경우에는 혹시 세미콜론 <code class=\"language-text\">;</code>을 빼먹지는 않았는지 확인해보자. struct를 선언한 다음 선언을 종료하는 중괄호 끝에 세미콜론 <code class=\"language-text\">;</code>을 빼먹는 실수가 잦고, 또 찾기도 어렵다. 늘 문법적으로 유효한(valid) 코드를 작성하는데 유의하도록 한다</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>다음 메시지가 \"Output\" 창에 출력되면 정점 셰이더를 성공적으로 구현한 것이다</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Compiling vertex shader API(D3D) /../Default_DirectX_Effect/Pass 0/Vertex Shader/ ...success</code></pre></div>\n<h3>픽셀 셰이더 함수 구현: 색상 구하기</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>정점 셰이더를 성공적으로 구현했지만 \"Preview\" 창에는 까만 화면 외에 아무 것도 보이지 않는다. 당연히 이는 저자가 강조한대로 픽셀의 색을 반환하는 역할을 하는 픽셀 셰이더가 비어있기 때문이다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bd02df89f5f8309d43f55f5270571c7d/9b29b/vertex_shader_compiled.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"vertex_shader_compiled\"\n        title=\"vertex_shader_compiled\"\n        src=\"/static/bd02df89f5f8309d43f55f5270571c7d/5a190/vertex_shader_compiled.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bd02df89f5f8309d43f55f5270571c7d/772e8/vertex_shader_compiled.png 200w,\n/static/bd02df89f5f8309d43f55f5270571c7d/e17e5/vertex_shader_compiled.png 400w,\n/static/bd02df89f5f8309d43f55f5270571c7d/5a190/vertex_shader_compiled.png 800w,\n/static/bd02df89f5f8309d43f55f5270571c7d/c1b63/vertex_shader_compiled.png 1200w,\n/static/bd02df89f5f8309d43f55f5270571c7d/29007/vertex_shader_compiled.png 1600w,\n/static/bd02df89f5f8309d43f55f5270571c7d/9b29b/vertex_shader_compiled.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>이제 \"Pass 0\" 아래 \"Pixer Shader\"를 선택해 다음처럼 픽셀 셰이더를 작성하도록 하자. 픽셀 셰이더는 \"픽셀의 색을 반환\"해야 하므로 r, g, b, a 총 4개의 float 값을 가지는 색 값을 반환하며 이는 각각 빨간색(red), 초록색(green), 파란색(blue), 알파(alpha) 채널 값에 해당한다</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"hlsl\"><pre class=\"language-hlsl\"><code class=\"language-hlsl\"><span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span> <span class=\"token function\">ps_main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> COLOR\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token number\">1.0f</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.0f</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.0f</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1.0f</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">error X3000: syntax error: unexpected token &#39;f&#39;</code> 에러가 발생하는 경우에는 혹시 마침표 <code class=\"language-text\">.</code>를 쉼표 <code class=\"language-text\">,</code>로 잘못 적거나 혹은 이 반대로 기입하지 않았는지 다시 한번 확인한다</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>완성된 \"진짜 쉬운 빨강 셰이더\"</h3>\n<p>마침내 **\"진짜 쉬운 빨강 셰이더\"**가 완성되었다. 다들 각자 생애 첫 셰이더를 만든 기쁨을 만끽하도록 하자</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a208ebbb0d23a1d5e57c5e967017db53/9b29b/complete_easiest_red_shader.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"complete_easiest_red_shader\"\n        title=\"complete_easiest_red_shader\"\n        src=\"/static/a208ebbb0d23a1d5e57c5e967017db53/5a190/complete_easiest_red_shader.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a208ebbb0d23a1d5e57c5e967017db53/772e8/complete_easiest_red_shader.png 200w,\n/static/a208ebbb0d23a1d5e57c5e967017db53/e17e5/complete_easiest_red_shader.png 400w,\n/static/a208ebbb0d23a1d5e57c5e967017db53/5a190/complete_easiest_red_shader.png 800w,\n/static/a208ebbb0d23a1d5e57c5e967017db53/c1b63/complete_easiest_red_shader.png 1200w,\n/static/a208ebbb0d23a1d5e57c5e967017db53/29007/complete_easiest_red_shader.png 1600w,\n/static/a208ebbb0d23a1d5e57c5e967017db53/9b29b/complete_easiest_red_shader.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>만약 실습을 진행하는데 어려움이 있는 경우에는 미리 완성된 다음 프로젝트 파일을 다운로드 받은 뒤 렌더몽키를 통해 열고 직접 분석해보도록 한다: <a href=\"https://github.com/sungkukpark/shader_programming_intro/blob/master/samples/easiest_red_shader/easiest_red_shader.zip\">다운로드 받기</a></p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"[Shader] Pope Kim의 셰이더 프로그래밍 입문 (2): 진짜 쉬운 빨강 셰이더"},"excerpt":"본 포스팅은 Pope Kim의 『셰이더 프로그래밍 입문 (한빛미디어, 2012)』의 Part 1의 Chapter 2에 해당하는 내용(p. 46-74)을 요약하기 위해 작성되었다. Pope Kim…"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/shader_programming_intro_2/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216","63159454"]}